name: Boys VS Girls Game
description:
So someone asked in a group if anyone could make this TikTok game  for him. I texted him and said I could make it.

He had to pay me for the game.

I was updating him with videos  of the game.

When I finished making it, sent a video of it and asked if it was good, he said he didn't want it anymore.

So I have no idea what to do with this game so maybe someone likes it!

It is a  TikTok game where boys and girls compete each other in wall pushing.
